<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Payment successful</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #3b1f0e; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .header p { color: #c9a97a; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .body { padding: 32px 40px; }
    .body p { color: #444444; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px; }
    .order-id { font-family: monospace; background: #f4f4f4; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #333; }
    .amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #3b1f0e; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payment successful ☕</h1>
      <p>Thank you for your order!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>
        We've received your payment for order <span class="order-id">{{orderId}}</span>.
        Your order is now being processed.
      </p>
      <div class="amount">{{amount}}</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#888888;text-align:center;">
        Keep this email as your payment confirmation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      You received this email because a payment was made on your account. If this wasn't you, please contact support.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
